{"id":1038990171,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"2 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1693708468,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"164 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1038990171/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"  Count Symmetric Integers","memory":"6.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int countSymmetricIntegers(int low, int high) {\n        int count = 0;\n\n    for (int num = low; num <= high; ++num) {\n        std::string str = std::to_string(num);\n        int n = str.length() ;\n        if(n%2!=0)continue;\n        n=n/2;\n        \n        int firstHalfSum = 0;\n        int secondHalfSum = 0;\n\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {\n            firstHalfSum += (str[i] - '0');\n            secondHalfSum += (str[n + i] - '0');\n        }\n\n        if (firstHalfSum == secondHalfSum) {\n            count++;\n        }\n    }\n\n    return count;\n\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"count-symmetric-integers","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
